hostResourcesTypesModule.description:
This MIB module registers type definitions for
      storage types, device types, and file system types.

      After the initial revision, this module will be
      maintained by IANA.

hrStorageOther.name: hrStorageOther
hrStorageOther.description:
The storage type identifier used when no other defined
        type is appropriate.

hrStorageRam.name: hrStorageRam
hrStorageRam.description: The storage type identifier used for RAM.

hrStorageVirtualMemory.name: hrStorageVirtualMemory
hrStorageVirtualMemory.description:
The storage type identifier used for virtual memory,
        temporary storage of swapped or paged memory.

hrStorageFixedDisk.name: hrStorageFixedDisk
hrStorageFixedDisk.description:
The storage type identifier used for non-removable
        rigid rotating magnetic storage devices.

hrStorageRemovableDisk.name: hrStorageRemovableDisk
hrStorageRemovableDisk.description:
The storage type identifier used for removable rigid
        rotating magnetic storage devices.

hrStorageFloppyDisk.name: hrStorageFloppyDisk
hrStorageFloppyDisk.description:
The storage type identifier used for non-rigid rotating
        magnetic storage devices.

hrStorageCompactDisc.name: hrStorageCompactDisc
hrStorageCompactDisc.description:
The storage type identifier used for read-only rotating
        optical storage devices.

hrStorageRamDisk.name: hrStorageRamDisk
hrStorageRamDisk.description:
The storage type identifier used for a file system that
        is stored in RAM.

hrStorageFlashMemory.name: hrStorageFlashMemory
hrStorageFlashMemory.description: The storage type identifier used for flash memory.

hrStorageNetworkDisk.name: hrStorageNetworkDisk
hrStorageNetworkDisk.description:
The storage type identifier used for a
        networked file system.

hrDeviceOther.name: hrDeviceOther
hrDeviceOther.description:
The device type identifier used when no other defined
        type is appropriate.

hrDeviceUnknown.name: hrDeviceUnknown
hrDeviceUnknown.description:
The device type identifier used when the device type is
        unknown.

hrDeviceProcessor.name: hrDeviceProcessor
hrDeviceProcessor.description: The device type identifier used for a CPU.

hrDeviceNetwork.name: hrDeviceNetwork
hrDeviceNetwork.description: The device type identifier used for a network interface.

hrDevicePrinter.name: hrDevicePrinter
hrDevicePrinter.description: The device type identifier used for a printer.

hrDeviceDiskStorage.name: hrDeviceDiskStorage
hrDeviceDiskStorage.description: The device type identifier used for a disk drive.

hrDeviceVideo.name: hrDeviceVideo
hrDeviceVideo.description: The device type identifier used for a video device.

hrDeviceAudio.name: hrDeviceAudio
hrDeviceAudio.description: The device type identifier used for an audio device.

hrDeviceCoprocessor.name: hrDeviceCoprocessor
hrDeviceCoprocessor.description: The device type identifier used for a co-processor.

hrDeviceKeyboard.name: hrDeviceKeyboard
hrDeviceKeyboard.description: The device type identifier used for a keyboard device.

hrDeviceModem.name: hrDeviceModem
hrDeviceModem.description: The device type identifier used for a modem.

hrDeviceParallelPort.name: hrDeviceParallelPort
hrDeviceParallelPort.description: The device type identifier used for a parallel port.

hrDevicePointing.name: hrDevicePointing
hrDevicePointing.description:
The device type identifier used for a pointing device
        (e.g., a mouse).

hrDeviceSerialPort.name: hrDeviceSerialPort
hrDeviceSerialPort.description: The device type identifier used for a serial port.

hrDeviceTape.name: hrDeviceTape
hrDeviceTape.description: The device type identifier used for a tape storage device.

hrDeviceClock.name: hrDeviceClock
hrDeviceClock.description: The device type identifier used for a clock device.

hrDeviceVolatileMemory.name: hrDeviceVolatileMemory
hrDeviceVolatileMemory.description:
The device type identifier used for a volatile memory
        storage device.

hrDeviceNonVolatileMemory.name: hrDeviceNonVolatileMemory
hrDeviceNonVolatileMemory.description:
The device type identifier used for a non-volatile memory

        storage device.
